<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionIRI> <https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/0.1.0> .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#imports> <https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/> .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.ontologyrepository.com/CommonCoreOntologies/ont00001754> "https://github.com/ucf-photovoltaics/pv-ontology"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#anyURI> .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "PV-Collada Ontology"@en .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#seeAlso> <http://www.example.com/pvcollada> .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "OWL 2 ontology derived from the PV-Collada 2.0 XSD schema. Provides vocabulary for PV system circuit topology, physical layout geometry, and component product data, within the MDS-Onto builtenv domain."@en .
<https://cwrusdle.bitbucket.io/mds/builtenv/pvcollada/> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#scopeNote> "Covers three interlocking layers: (1) a product library of typed PV components (modules, inverters, cables, etc.); (2) a circuit topology describing how those components are wired together; and (3) a physical 3-D layout associating circuit positions with geometric rack instances. ModuleLayout is the cross-domain bridge between layers 2 and 3."@en .
